569
00:25:57,539 --> 00:25:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] Vremenom,

570
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:01,339
[SPEAKER_01] čitajući jako mnogo knjiga

571
00:26:01,339 --> 00:26:02,339
[SPEAKER_01] kao tineđer,

572
00:26:02,339 --> 00:26:03,779
[SPEAKER_01] pa u 20. godinama,

573
00:26:03,779 --> 00:26:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] pa putujući mnogo,

574
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] znate,

575
00:26:05,559 --> 00:26:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] stotinu zemalja nije malo.

576
00:26:07,940 --> 00:26:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pa susrećući se

577
00:26:09,460 --> 00:26:10,819
[SPEAKER_01] sa različitim ljudima,

578
00:26:11,019 --> 00:26:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] na jedan put

579
00:26:12,619 --> 00:26:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] to vas počinje oblikovati.

580
00:26:15,180 --> 00:26:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] Prije 20 godina

581
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam otkriju

582
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:19,400
[SPEAKER_01] Bosanske piramide,

583
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,839
[SPEAKER_01] što mene interesiralo

584
00:26:20,839 --> 00:26:21,819
[SPEAKER_01] je vjerovno kazati

585
00:26:21,819 --> 00:26:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] da imamo građevenu,

586
00:26:22,980 --> 00:26:24,759
[SPEAKER_01] pa smo geometrija,

587
00:26:24,759 --> 00:26:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] pa orientacija

588
00:26:25,579 --> 00:26:26,720
[SPEAKER_01] primastrana svijeta,

589
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:27,799
[SPEAKER_01] pa našli beton,

590
00:26:27,799 --> 00:26:28,900
[SPEAKER_01] pa ga analizirali,

591
00:26:28,900 --> 00:26:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] najkvalitetniji beton na svijetu,

592
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:32,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa dakle fizički aspekt.

593
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:35,220
[SPEAKER_01] Onda druge te znanosti,

594
00:26:35,220 --> 00:26:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] druge nauke,

595
00:26:36,099 --> 00:26:37,019
[SPEAKER_01] geofizika,

596
00:26:37,019 --> 00:26:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] energetska snimanja,

597
00:26:38,460 --> 00:26:39,480
[SPEAKER_01] datiranje,

598
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,900
[SPEAKER_01] na jedan put raste,

599
00:26:41,019 --> 00:26:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] pa na jedan put svajte,

600
00:26:42,059 --> 00:26:42,359
[SPEAKER_01] hej,

601
00:26:42,359 --> 00:26:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] energijski aspekt,

602
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] piramida,

603
00:26:44,079 --> 00:26:46,160
[SPEAKER_01] energijski polačivač,

604
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,259
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda energija

605
00:26:47,259 --> 00:26:48,279
[SPEAKER_01] utječe na nas,

606
00:26:48,279 --> 00:26:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] utječe na naše zdravlje,

607
00:26:49,519 --> 00:26:50,759
[SPEAKER_01] to je četvrti aspekt,

608
00:26:50,759 --> 00:26:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] pa utječe na našu duhovnost.

609
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:54,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ne duhovnost,

610
00:26:54,299 --> 00:26:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] kao što smo nas nekada

611
00:26:55,420 --> 00:26:56,240
[SPEAKER_01] učili u školama.

612
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,299
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, duhovnost,

613
00:26:57,299 --> 00:26:58,220
[SPEAKER_01] to vam je religija,

614
00:26:58,220 --> 00:26:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] religioznost.

615
00:26:59,220 --> 00:27:01,339
[SPEAKER_01] Religija je nešto posebno.

616
00:27:01,339 --> 00:27:02,900
[SPEAKER_01] Duhovnost je razvoj

617
00:27:02,900 --> 00:27:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] duhovnih čula,

618
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:06,299
[SPEAKER_01] da možete da spoznate

619
00:27:06,299 --> 00:27:09,480
[SPEAKER_01] svijet van fizičkog.

620
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] fizički spoznajemo

621
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:13,240
[SPEAKER_01] puta naš pet fizičkih čula.

622
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] Mi možemo da vidimo,

623
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,200
[SPEAKER_01] da čujemo,

624
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] da osjetimo njuh,

625
00:27:17,079 --> 00:27:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] miris,

626
00:27:17,619 --> 00:27:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno okus,

627
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:21,200
[SPEAKER_01] ali osim tih pet,

628
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:23,319
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo limitiranih čula,

629
00:27:23,319 --> 00:27:25,279
[SPEAKER_01] imamo i 30 duhovnih čula.

630
00:27:25,279 --> 00:27:27,299
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo da osjetimo energiju,

631
00:27:27,299 --> 00:27:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] možemo da vidimo energiju,

632
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,660
[SPEAKER_01] možemo da imamo boje,

633
00:27:30,660 --> 00:27:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] aura, čakri.

634
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:34,519
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo da postanemo svjesni

635
00:27:34,519 --> 00:27:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] tog drugog energijskog aspekta.

636
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:38,839
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo da komuniciramo mislima,

637
00:27:38,839 --> 00:27:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] telepatija je također,

638
00:27:40,079 --> 00:27:41,059
[SPEAKER_01] duhovno čulo.

639
00:27:41,059 --> 00:27:43,259
[SPEAKER_01] Putujući svijetom,

640
00:27:43,259 --> 00:27:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

641
00:27:43,579 --> 00:27:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] Anasazi,

642
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] ili američki indijanci,

643
00:27:46,779 --> 00:27:49,740
[SPEAKER_01] ili originalni ljudi u Australiji,

644
00:27:49,740 --> 00:27:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji su Anglezi nazvali

645
00:27:52,059 --> 00:27:53,259
[SPEAKER_01] ab original,

646
00:27:53,259 --> 00:27:54,140
[SPEAKER_01] ab origini,

647
00:27:54,140 --> 00:27:55,299
[SPEAKER_01] ab original,

648
00:27:55,299 --> 00:27:57,819
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ne originalni.

649
00:27:57,819 --> 00:27:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] Krivo.

650
00:27:58,539 --> 00:28:00,640
[SPEAKER_01] Anglezi su ilegali imikranti.

651
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:03,259
[SPEAKER_01] A ovo su originalni.

652
00:28:03,259 --> 00:28:05,660
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, oni su svi znali

653
00:28:05,660 --> 00:28:07,759
[SPEAKER_01] za moć intencije,

654
00:28:07,759 --> 00:28:09,240
[SPEAKER_01] moć namjere.

655
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ako imaju 3, 4, 5 meseci suhove,

656
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:15,140
[SPEAKER_01] počinju da prizivaju kišu.

657
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:17,240
[SPEAKER_01] Izbilja kiša počinje da pada.

658
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:18,700
[SPEAKER_01] Neko sa plesom,

659
00:28:18,700 --> 00:28:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] neko sa molitvama.

660
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

661
00:28:21,039 --> 00:28:23,119
[SPEAKER_01] i to je duhovno čulo.

662
00:28:23,119 --> 00:28:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] Neki mi je nazvali telekineza,

663
00:28:26,099 --> 00:28:27,640
[SPEAKER_01] mogu da pomjeraju objekte

664
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] snagom svoje namjere.

665
00:28:30,579 --> 00:28:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] Teleportacija,

666
00:28:33,059 --> 00:28:34,359
[SPEAKER_01] kretanje kroz prostor,

667
00:28:34,359 --> 00:28:36,279
[SPEAKER_01] vreme kojega smo se malo dotakli.

668
00:28:36,279 --> 00:28:38,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je sve duhovna čula.

669
00:28:38,420 --> 00:28:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što rekoh,

670
00:28:40,079 --> 00:28:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] pri 20 godina nisam razmišljao

671
00:28:42,599 --> 00:28:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] o ovom aspektu,

672
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] ali vremenom i kroz ovaj projekat

673
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:46,839
[SPEAKER_01] sam rastao,

674
00:28:46,839 --> 00:28:48,940
[SPEAKER_01] susretao se s velikim brojem ljudi,

675
00:28:48,940 --> 00:28:49,859
[SPEAKER_01] učio.

676
00:28:49,859 --> 00:28:51,279
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek kažem za sebe

677
00:28:51,279 --> 00:28:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja najblagoslovljeniji čovjek na svijetu

678
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:57,059
[SPEAKER_01] jer sam bio u prilici na najviše.

679
00:28:57,059 --> 00:28:59,819
[SPEAKER_01] Da nauči mi to zbilja utiče na moj rast

680
00:28:59,819 --> 00:29:01,359
[SPEAKER_01] i to je odgovor na vaše pitanje

681
00:29:01,359 --> 00:29:02,480
[SPEAKER_01] šta je najviše ucalo.

682
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:04,200
[SPEAKER_01] Sve nekako oko mene,

683
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:05,460
[SPEAKER_01] taj čitav kontekst

684
00:29:05,460 --> 00:29:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] i naravno moja otvrnost da primam znanje.

685
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] A onda, što više informacije imate,

686
00:29:12,099 --> 00:29:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] postaje vam sve očiglednije koliko malo znate.

687
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:18,740
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno u ovom momentu na planetu

688
00:29:18,740 --> 00:29:21,259
[SPEAKER_01] nema čovjeka koji je obišao i istraživao

689
00:29:21,259 --> 00:29:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] više piramide od mene.

690
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:26,619
[SPEAKER_01] U Egiptu, vi pročitate neznanstvenu Wikipediju,

691
00:29:26,619 --> 00:29:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] kaže ima 118 piramida.

692
00:29:28,619 --> 00:29:31,859
[SPEAKER_01] To će vam isto potvrditi umjetna inteligencija.

693
00:29:31,859 --> 00:29:32,859
[SPEAKER_01] 118.

694
00:29:32,859 --> 00:29:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ih obišao i istraživao 155.

695
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:37,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ali manje više zato.

696
00:29:37,380 --> 00:29:41,180
[SPEAKER_01] Svatite da ono što vas uče je krivo.

697
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] U Kini 250 bio sam treći stranac

698
00:29:44,380 --> 00:29:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] koji je obišao njihove piramide.

699
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:49,160
[SPEAKER_01] U Indoneziji, u Kambođi,

700
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,700
[SPEAKER_01] u Mauriciju, u Kanariju,

701
00:29:50,700 --> 00:29:53,240
[SPEAKER_01] na Peru, u Bolivijama, doktorska piramida.

702
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:55,700
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vjerojatno nema čovjeka

703
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] kojih je više sva živao od mene,

704
00:29:57,119 --> 00:29:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] pisao o njima.

705
00:29:58,019 --> 00:30:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] A da mi vi sad pitate

706
00:30:01,019 --> 00:30:03,359
[SPEAKER_01] ko je gradio Egipatske piramide,

707
00:30:03,359 --> 00:30:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću vam iskreno reći da ne znam.

708
00:30:05,559 --> 00:30:08,660
[SPEAKER_01] Niti kada su točno građeni,

709
00:30:08,660 --> 00:30:10,900
[SPEAKER_01] niti kako su građeni,

710
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] niti zašto.

711
00:30:12,539 --> 00:30:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo da špekuliramo.

712
00:30:15,539 --> 00:30:19,160
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, bajkice koje nam serviraju

713
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:22,059
[SPEAKER_01] kroz obrazni sustav da se to gradila

714
00:30:22,059 --> 00:30:23,700
[SPEAKER_01] faraonska civilizacija,

715
00:30:23,700 --> 00:30:25,799
[SPEAKER_01] četvrte dinastije,

716
00:30:25,799 --> 00:30:27,319
[SPEAKER_01] Keopske, Efra i Mikere,

717
00:30:27,319 --> 00:30:30,700
[SPEAKER_01] nemaju niti jednog jedinog znanstvenog argumenta.

718
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:33,819
[SPEAKER_01] To da je bilo pre 4.500 godina,

719
00:30:33,819 --> 00:30:34,799
[SPEAKER_01] to nije sigurno,

720
00:30:34,799 --> 00:30:35,799
[SPEAKER_01] to sam vidio sam.

721
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:37,259
[SPEAKER_01] Dođete na platu Gize,

722
00:30:37,259 --> 00:30:41,920
[SPEAKER_01] imate nekoliko podzemnih struktura tamo

723
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] koje su uplavljene,

724
00:30:43,019 --> 00:30:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] morska voda.

725
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] Giza je 180 km daleko od Mediterana,

726
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:50,599
[SPEAKER_01] kada je zadnji put bila velika poplava,

727
00:30:50,599 --> 00:30:51,839
[SPEAKER_01] prije 12.000 godina,

728
00:30:51,839 --> 00:30:53,359
[SPEAKER_01] sa krajem zadnjeg gledanog doba.

729
00:30:53,359 --> 00:30:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] I to je razlog zbog čega

730
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] egiptolozi ne otvaraju te podzemne

731
00:30:57,619 --> 00:30:59,859
[SPEAKER_01] strukture,

732
00:30:59,859 --> 00:31:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] kao što, recimo,

733
00:31:00,680 --> 00:31:02,779
[SPEAKER_01] komora,

734
00:31:02,779 --> 00:31:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] kako mi kažu,

735
00:31:04,460 --> 00:31:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] kralja Tota.

736
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] Tota je bio njihovo božanstvo

737
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:09,680
[SPEAKER_01] i najvjerojatniji dizajn jer piramida.

738
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:13,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali njihova faza bogova je

739
00:31:13,079 --> 00:31:15,599
[SPEAKER_01] od 43.000 godina

740
00:31:15,599 --> 00:31:19,819
[SPEAKER_01] pa do prije oprilike 20.000 godina.

741
00:31:19,819 --> 00:31:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, na jedan put vi vidite,

742
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:23,019
[SPEAKER_01] skrivaju se informacije,

743
00:31:23,019 --> 00:31:24,220
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je puno starije.

744
00:31:24,220 --> 00:31:26,160
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

745
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:29,240
[SPEAKER_01] ko, kada, kako, zašto?

746
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] Neodgovoreno.

747
00:31:30,539 --> 00:31:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ako pita ko je gradio piramidno u Meksiku,

748
00:31:33,119 --> 00:31:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] Toti Hakan,

749
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:35,160
[SPEAKER_01] također ne znam.

750
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:37,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali znam da ih nisu gradili Tolteci.

751
00:31:37,619 --> 00:31:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je neko pita koje gradio piramide na Kanarima.

752
00:31:40,460 --> 00:31:42,299
[SPEAKER_01] 104 piramide imaju.

753
00:31:42,299 --> 00:31:45,440
[SPEAKER_01] Najvjerojatnije guanči

754
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,180
[SPEAKER_01] koji imaju direktno porijeklo

755
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] od civilizacije

756
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:50,660
[SPEAKER_01] od prije kraja za negledanog doba

757
00:31:50,660 --> 00:31:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] koja je življela u Atlantiku.

758
00:31:51,779 --> 00:31:52,400
[SPEAKER_01] Koja je to?

759
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:54,180
[SPEAKER_01] Pa često se govori o Atlantidi.

760
00:31:54,180 --> 00:31:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] Na Mauriciju su sedam piramida.

761
00:31:57,119 --> 00:32:00,339
[SPEAKER_01] Pogledate sve ove naše enziklopedije.

762
00:32:00,339 --> 00:32:03,019
[SPEAKER_01] Izvore informacija.

763
00:32:03,019 --> 00:32:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] kaže da do 15. ostojeća tamo niko nije živio.

764
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:07,740
[SPEAKER_01] Pre su došli bijeli evropljani

765
00:32:07,740 --> 00:32:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] koji nisu gradili piramide.

766
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:11,099
[SPEAKER_01] A piramide su tu.

767
00:32:11,099 --> 00:32:14,259
[SPEAKER_01] Bio, provjerio, izračno, analizirao

768
00:32:14,259 --> 00:32:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] 20.000 tona materijala.

769
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:17,819
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kao što reku,

770
00:32:17,819 --> 00:32:20,799
[SPEAKER_01] koliko god dobivate informacija

771
00:32:20,799 --> 00:32:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] i mislite da nešto znate,

772
00:32:22,980 --> 00:32:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo tek onda shvatite koliko malo znate.

773
00:32:26,799 --> 00:32:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što im je zajedničko?

774
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:29,160
[SPEAKER_01] U piramidama.

775
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, moja klasifikacija je drugačija

776
00:32:32,599 --> 00:32:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] nego što nas uči u školama.

777
